# Discord macro for DiceParser Discord bot. Docs: https://github.com/Rolisteam/DiceParser
# Just paste the below code in your Discor server.
#
# Usage: Type !tNN (where NN is your current skill/characteristic value), eg. !t67

!macro add t([0-9]+) "\1;1d100;$1-$2;($1|10)-($2|10);($2|10);$2-(($2|10)*10);\":game_die: [ $5$6 / ($1) ]\";$2i:[=100]{\":skull: Ouch! Critical failure!\"};$2i:[=1]{\":star_struck:  Great! Critical success!\"};$3i:[>=0]{\":white_check_mark: Test passed!  DoS: [ +$4 ]\"}{\":no_entry: Test failed   DoF.: [ $4 ]\"}" True
